::Feline::
She lay on the ground.  Her animal DNA was dissolving away from her robotic 
anatomy.  Soon, all would be left of her was a bot with no beast mode.  Her 
tracking beacon still pinged on. She thought she heard HotRod on her 
commlink, but with her mind being ravaged by pain, she dismissed it as her 
imagination running wild.

::KitKat::
She smiled at Darkmouse who sat across from her at the table.  "He's alive. 
That's one thing in our favor."  She responded to Drillbit. "Hello there. I 
will need your assistantce in the mess hall. Can you come and talk for a 
bit?"


::GoldenEye::

but I just got back from vacation and well, I'm rearing to go back to work."
